## 5. WHAT WAS BUILT

* FastAPI Signal Layer Backend
* Strict Signal Schema
* Deterministic Trace ID Generator
* CSV Based Real/Semi-real Data Ingestion
* Multi-Zone Signal Generation
* Multi-Domain Support
* API Layer
* Failure Handling
* Console Logging

---

## 6. FAILURE CASES

Handled cases:

* Invalid Zone ID
* Missing Dataset
* Corrupted CSV Data

Error Format:

```json
{
  "error": "INVALID_INPUT",
  "trace_id": "TRACE_xxxx"
}
```

